  "title": "Cleaner",
  "description": "<h2><strong>Position:</strong> Cleaner</h2><p><strong>Location:</strong> Singapore<br /><strong>Industry:</strong> Food & Beverage<br /><strong>Salary Range:</strong> SGD 1,800 – 2,000 per month</p><h3><strong>About Us</strong></h3><p>We are part of a dynamic restaurant group behind <strong>Altro Zafferano</strong>, <strong>Griglia Open Fire Italian Kitchen</strong>, and <strong>54 Steakhouse</strong>, recognised among Singapore’s leading dining destinations. We offer a <strong>stable and professional working environment</strong>, with opportunities for growth as the group continues to evolve.</p><h2><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Support the efficient and smooth operation of the restaurant by maintaining cleanliness across <strong>front-of-house (FOH) and back-of-house (BOH)</strong> areas</p></li><li><p>Clean internal and external restaurant areas, including dining areas, bar countertops, dishwashing areas, and common spaces</p></li><li><p>Collect, segregate, and dispose of trash and garbage in designated areas</p></li><li><p>Wash dishes, pots, pans, trays, and kitchen equipment manually or using dishwashing machines</p></li><li><p>Clean and maintain kitchen floors, drains, grease traps, worktables, sinks, walls, ceilings, air vents, and refrigerators</p></li><li><p>Ensure compliance with <strong>kitchen hygiene, food safety, and workplace safety standards</strong></p></li><li><p>Transfer supplies and equipment between storage and work areas as required</p></li><li><p>Maintain cleanliness of waste bins and surrounding areas</p></li><li><p>Report any issues or maintenance concerns to the <strong>Head Chef or Supervisor</strong></p></li><li><p>Maintain adequate stock levels of cleaning supplies and equipment</p></li></ul><h2><strong>Requirements</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Basic knowledge of <strong>cleaning, hygiene, and workplace safety practices</strong></p></li><li><p>Physically fit and able to perform manual work</p></li><li><p>Responsible, reliable, and able to work independently</p></li><li><p>Prior experience in <strong>F&B or hospitality</strong> is an advantage</p></li></ul><p><strong>Able to join immediately</strong></p>",
